<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Booking Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f5f7;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #222;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .booking-details {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .booking-details th,
    .booking-details td {
      padding: 14px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .booking-details th {
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .booking-details td {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #555;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .booking-details tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .booking-details td:first-child {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #007BFF;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Booking Confirmation</h2>
    <p>Thank you for booking with us! Below are the details of your booking:</p>

    <table class="booking-details">
      <tr>
        <th>Your Name</th>
        <td><%= name %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Your Email</th>
        <td><%= email %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Check-in Date</th>
        <td><%= checkin %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Check-out Date</th>
        <td><%= checkout %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Number of Adults</th>
        <td><%= adult %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Number of Children</th>
        <td><%= child %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Room Selection</th>
        <td><%= room %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Special Requests</th>
        <td><%= message || 'No special requests' %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes to your booking, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <a href="mailto:moruditech@gmail.com" class="cta-button">Contact Us</a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>We look forward to hosting you!</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>Your Golden Field Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
